PS等；娱乐游戏支持娱乐游戏应用下载及使用，如斗地主等；音乐壁画支持多媒体音乐播放，音乐壁画；</td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr></tbody></table><table width=\"880\"><tbody style=\";padding: 0px\"><tr style=\";padding: 0px\" class=\"firstRow\"><td width=\"59\" valign=\"middle\" rowspan=\"10\" style=\";padding: 0px;font-size: 12px;border-width: thin;border-top-style: none;border-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);text-align: center;vertical-align: middle\">8</td><td width=\"79\" valign=\"middle\" rowspan=\"10\" style=\";padding: 0px;font-size: 12px;border-width: thin;border-top-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);text-align: center;vertical-align: middle\">语言</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\";padding: 0px\">中英文切换支持中文、英文两国语言；</td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: 微软雅黑, arial;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><br/></p><table width=\"880\"><tbody style=\";padding: 0px\"><tr style=\";padding: 0px\" class=\"firstRow\"><td width=\"59\" valign=\"middle\" rowspan=\"10\" style=\";padding: 0px;font-size: 12px;border-width: thin;border-top-style: none;border-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);text-align: center;vertical-align: middle\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-size: small\">9</span></td><td width=\"79\" valign=\"middle\" rowspan=\"10\" style=\";padding: 0px;font-size: 12px;border-width: thin;border-top-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);text-align: center;vertical-align: middle\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-size: small\">智能应用类</span></td><td valign=\"top\" style=\";padding: 0px\">自动开关机智能应用类业务支持机顶盒、电视自动开机关机功能，对于监区里面的机顶盒，可以通过后台进行开机关机控制；狱警宿舍区自动WIFI无线覆盖智能互动控制器能够自动为监区管理员宿舍或办公区提供无线信号，而不需要另外再部署无线设备；</td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr><tr><td><br/></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span style=\";padding: 0px;font-family: 微软雅黑, arial;font-size: small;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><br/></span><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.szhhzt.com/images/upload/image/20171122/20171122112838_25026.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p>', '', '1', '17', '1');
INSERT INTO `message` VALUES ('137153', '云威榜“互联网+智慧工厂”大数据解决方案', '1542720884538.jpg', '2018-11-20', '<p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720817901098907.jpg\" height=\"286px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">智能制造工业大数据是工业企业的重要资产，是企业实现转型升级的核心要素。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">本方案基于工业大数据，综合提出“互联网+智慧工厂”大数据平台解决方案，为大数据智能工厂的规划提供参考。</p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720818684099761.jpg\" height=\"402px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720819125001398.jpg\" height=\"340px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720819543030866.jpg\" height=\"312px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720820116074277.jpg\" height=\"355px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720820543072423.jpg\" height=\"279px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720820895098414.jpg\" height=\"316px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720821423039508.jpg\" height=\"284px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720822154019036.jpg\" height=\"387px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720822696041333.jpg\" height=\"303px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720823371090948.jpg\" height=\"332px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720824078099157.jpg\" height=\"329px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720824554027287.jpg\" height=\"339px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720825786042648.jpg\" height=\"333px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720826506053452.jpg\" height=\"340px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720827556062215.jpg\" height=\"339px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720828735020341.jpg\" height=\"340px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720829244061290.jpg\" height=\"388px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720829684036546.jpg\" height=\"331px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720830369022196.jpg\" height=\"332px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720830780037871.jpg\" height=\"348px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">结语</p><p style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">近年来，“机器人换人”项目已在中国各处开展，工业自动化、数字化作为“智能制造”的关键技术，工业大数据已成为企业的生存存在业态，在新一轮智能制造发展浪潮中起重要作用。</p><p><br/></p>', '', '1', '18', '1');
INSERT INTO `message` VALUES ('137154', '这一次，华为重新定义园区', '1542721399758.jpg', '2018-11-20', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.5;\">园区是人们工作与生活的重要载体。智慧园区运用云计算、物联网、大数据、人工智能等新ICT技术, 解决传统园区正面临的“管理效率低、服务体验差、能源浪费大、综合安防弱、运营成本高”等痛点，实现面向行业的园区数字化转型，赋能产业创新发展和服务体验升级。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.5;\">华为致力于打造智慧园区数字化使能平台，重新定义园区业务架构，向下汇聚各类智能前端子系统，向上支撑生态伙伴创新应用开发，实现园区“数据全融合、状态全可视、业务全可管、事件全可控”。通过“安全、舒适、高效、绿色”的智慧园区理念，为园区使用者提供更优质的服务体验，为园区运营者提供持续卓越运营的能力，从而创造更大的经济与社会价值。</p><p><a class=\"hw-btn btn-empty-black font-medium mlr10 mr20-wap \" href=\"https://e.huawei.com/cn/videos/industries/2018/201810171133\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px 0px; padding: 9px 30px; box-sizing: border-box; cursor: pointer; text-decoration-line: none; outline-style: none; transition: none 0s ease 0s; border-radius: 2px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.125; position: relative; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border: 2px solid rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\">智慧园区@全联接大会</span></a></p><p><a class=\"social-share-icon icon-email\" href=\"mailto:information%40huawei.com?subject=%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E5%9B%AD%E5%8C%BA%20-%20%E5%8D%8E%E4%B8%BA%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88&body=https%3A%2F%2Fe.huawei.com%2Fcn%2Fsolutions%2Findustries%2Fsmart-city%2Fcampus%0A%E5%8D%8E%E4%B8%BA%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E5%9B%AD%E5%8C%BA%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E4%BA%91%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E3%80%81%E7%89%A9%E8%81%94%E7%BD%91%E7%AD%89%E5%85%88%E8%BF%9B%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%EF%BC%8C%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%9B%AD%E5%8C%BA%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E6%94%AF%E6%92%91%E5%92%8C%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E6%94%AF%E6%92%91%E4%B8%A4%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%EF%BC%8C%E9%87%8D%E7%82%B9%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%AE%89%E9%98%B2%E3%80%81%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E7%89%A9%E7%AE%A1