62215.jpg\" height=\"339px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720828735020341.jpg\" height=\"340px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720829244061290.jpg\" height=\"388px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720829684036546.jpg\" height=\"331px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720830369022196.jpg\" height=\"332px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720830780037871.jpg\" height=\"348px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">结语</p><p style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">近年来，“机器人换人”项目已在中国各处开展，工业自动化、数字化作为“智能制造”的关键技术，工业大数据已成为企业的生存存在业态，在新一轮智能制造发展浪潮中起重要作用。</p><p><br/></p>', '', '1', '18', '1');
INSERT INTO `message` VALUES ('137168', '云威榜“互联网+智慧工厂”大数据解决方案', '1542720884538.jpg', '2018-11-20', '<p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720817901098907.jpg\" height=\"286px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">智能制造工业大数据是工业企业的重要资产，是企业实现转型升级的核心要素。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">本方案基于工业大数据，综合提出“互联网+智慧工厂”大数据平台解决方案，为大数据智能工厂的规划提供参考。</p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720818684099761.jpg\" height=\"402px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720819125001398.jpg\" height=\"340px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720819543030866.jpg\" height=\"312px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720820116074277.jpg\" height=\"355px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720820543072423.jpg\" height=\"279px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720820895098414.jpg\" height=\"316px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720821423039508.jpg\" height=\"284px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720822154019036.jpg\" height=\"387px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720822696041333.jpg\" height=\"303px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720823371090948.jpg\" height=\"332px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720824078099157.jpg\" height=\"329px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720824554027287.jpg\" height=\"339px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720825786042648.jpg\" height=\"333px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720826506053452.jpg\" height=\"340px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720827556062215.jpg\" height=\"339px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720828735020341.jpg\" height=\"340px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720829244061290.jpg\" height=\"388px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720829684036546.jpg\" height=\"331px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720830369022196.jpg\" height=\"332px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720830780037871.jpg\" height=\"348px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">结语</p><p style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">近年来，“机器人换人”项目已在中国各处开展，工业自动化、数字化作为“智能制造”的关键技术，工业大数据已成为企业的生存存在业态，在新一轮智能制造发展浪潮中起重要作用。</p><p><br/></p>', '', '1', '18', '1');
INSERT INTO `message` VALUES ('137169', '这一次，华为重新定义园区', '1542721399758.jpg', '2018-11-20', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.5;\">园区是人们工作与生活的重要载体。智慧园区运用云计算、物联网、大数据、人工智能等新ICT技术, 解决传统园区正面临的“管理效率低、服务体验差、能源浪费大、综合安防弱、运营成本高”等痛点，实现面向行业的园区数字化转型，赋能产业创新发展和服务体验升级。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.5;\">华为致力于打造智慧园区数字化使能平台，重新定义园区业务架构，向下汇聚各类智能前端子系统，向上支撑生态伙伴创新应用开发，实现园区“数据全融合、状态全可视、业务全可管、事件全可控”。通过“安全、舒适、高效、绿色”的智慧园区理念，为园区使用者提供更优质的服务体验，为园区运营者提供持续卓越运营的能力，从而创造更大的经济与社会价值。</p><p><a class=\"hw-btn btn-empty-black font-medium mlr10 mr20-wap \" href=\"https://e.huawei.com/cn/videos/industries/2018/201810171133\" style=\"margin: 20px 10px 0px; padding: 9px 30px; box-sizing: border-box; cursor: pointer; text-decoration-line: none; outline-style: none; transition: none 0s ease 0s; border-radius: 2px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.125; position: relative; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border: 2px solid rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\">智慧园区@全联接大会</span></a></p><p><a class=\"social-share-icon icon-email\" href=\"mailto:information%40huawei.com?subject=%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E5%9B%AD%E5%8C%BA%20-%20%E5%8D%8E%E4%B8%BA%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88&body=https%3A%2F%2Fe.huawei.com%2Fcn%2Fsolutions%2Findustries%2Fsmart-city%2Fcampus%0A%E5%8D%8E%E4%B8%BA%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E5%9B%AD%E5%8C%BA%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E4%BA%91%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E3%80%81%E7%89%A9%E8%81%94%E7%BD%91%E7%AD%89%E5%85%88%E8%BF%9B%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%EF%BC%8C%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%9B%AD%E5%8C%BA%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E6%94%AF%E6%92%91%E5%92%8C%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E6%94%AF%E6%92%91%E4%B8%A4%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%EF%BC%8C%E9%87%8D%E7%82%B9%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%AE%89%E9%98%B2%E3%80%81%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E7%89%A9%E7%AE%A1%E5%92%8C%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9E%E5%85%AC%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E5%8C%85%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BA%E5%9B%AD%E5%8C%BA%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E8%80%85%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%A5%E9%A9%BB%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E4%BE%BF%E5%88%A9%EF%BC%8C%E5%A2%9E%E5%BC%BA%E5%9B%AD%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E7%AB%9E%E4%BA%89%E5%8A%9B%E5%92%8C%E8%BE%90%E5%B0%84%E5%B8%A6%E5%8A%A8%E5%8A%9B%E3%80%82\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -1px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; cursor: pointer; text-decoration-line: none; outline-style: none; transition: all 0.4s ease 0s; position: relative; display: inline-block; width: 50px; height: 32px;\"><span class=\"iconfont icon-share-email\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; transition: all 0.4s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; position: absolute; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); top: 17px; left: 17px; font-family: iconfont !important;\"></span></a><a class=\"social-share-icon icon-linkedin\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&ro=true&title=%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E5%9B%AD%E5%8C%BA%20-%20%E5%8D%8E%E4%B8%BA%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88&url=https%3A%2F%2Fe.huawei.com%2Fcn%2Fsolutions%2Findustries%2Fsmart-city%2Fcampus&summary=%E5%8D%8E%E4%B8%BA%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E5%9B%AD%E5%8C%BA%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E4%BA%91%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E3%80%81%E7%89%A9%E8%81%94%E7%BD%91%E7%AD%89%E5%85%88%E8%BF%9B%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%EF%BC%8C%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%9B%AD%E5%8C%BA%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E6%94%AF%E6%92%91%E5%92%8C%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E6%94%AF%E6%92%91%E4%B8%A4%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%EF%BC%8C%E9%87%8D%E7%82%B9%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E5%AE%89%E9%98%B2%E3%80%81%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E7%89%A9%E7%AE%A1%E5%92%8C%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9E%E5%85%AC%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E5%8C%85%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BA%E5%9B%AD%E5%8C%BA%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E8%80%85%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%A5%E9%A9%BB%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%