t;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">结语</p><p style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">近年来，“机器人换人”项目已在中国各处开展，工业自动化、数字化作为“智能制造”的关键技术，工业大数据已成为企业的生存存在业态，在新一轮智能制造发展浪潮中起重要作用。</p><p><br/></p>', '', '1', '18', '1');
INSERT INTO `message` VALUES ('137181', '云威榜“互联网+智慧工厂”大数据解决方案', '1542720884538.jpg', '2018-11-20', '<p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720817901098907.jpg\" height=\"286px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">智能制造工业大数据是工业企业的重要资产，是企业实现转型升级的核心要素。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">本方案基于工业大数据，综合提出“互联网+智慧工厂”大数据平台解决方案，为大数据智能工厂的规划提供参考。</p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720818684099761.jpg\" height=\"402px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542720819125001398.jpg\" height=\"340px\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"imgDiv\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0