t-size: 30px; line-height: 1.2; text-align: center;\">相关产品</h2><ul class=\"J-carousel-ul clearfix list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li><p><a class=\"box picImg2\" href=\"https://e.huawei.com/cn/products/enterprise-networking/routers/ne/ne40e\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; box-sizing: border-box; cursor: pointer; text-decoration-line: none; outline-style: none; transition: all 0.4s ease 0s; display: block;\"></a></p><p><a class=\"box picImg2\" href=\"https://e.huawei.com/cn/products/enterprise-networking/routers/ne/ne40e\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; box-sizing: border-box; cursor: pointer; text-decoration-line: none; outline-style: none; transition: all 0.4s ease 0s; display: block;\"><img class=\"J-V2Replaceimglazyload\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20181120/1542721391385059978.png\"/></a></p><h3 class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 400;\"><p><a class=\"box picImg2\" href=\"https://e.huawei.com/cn/products/enterprise-networking/routers/ne/ne40e\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; box-sizing: border-box; cursor: pointer; text-decoration-line: none; outline-style: none; transition: all 0.4s ease 0s; display: block;\">NE40E系列</a></p></h3><p class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.375; text-align: left; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><a class=\"box picImg2\" href=\"https://e.huawei.com/cn/products/enterprise-networking/routers/ne/ne40e\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; box-sizing: border-box; cursor: pointer; text-decoration-line: none; outline-style: none; transition: all 0.4s ease 0s; display: block;\"><br/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.375; text-align: left; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><a class=\"box picImg2\" href=\"https://